legs.start_address: Kefalonia International Airport Anna Pollatou, Kefalonia 281 00, Greece

steps.html_instructions: At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit and stay on EO Argostoliou Samis
EO Argostoliou Samis turns right and becomes Epar.Od. Argostoliou
Turn left onto Epar.Od. Davgaton - Dilinaton/Epar.Od. Faraklaton - Agias Efimias
Continue straight onto Epar.Od. Faraklaton - Agias Efimias
Turn right to stay on Epar.Od. Faraklaton - Agias Efimias

Take the Fiskardo - Vasiliki ferry to Vasiliki
Toll road
Turn right onto Epar.Od. Lefkas - Vasilikis/Epar.Od. Vasilikis - Marantochoriou

Turn left to stay on Epar.Od. Lefkas - Vasilikis/Epar.Od. Vasilikis - Marantochoriou
Continue to follow Epar.Od. Lefkas - Vasilikis
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Philosophorum
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Dimitroy Golemi

At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit and stay on E952
Toll road

Turn right onto Epar.Od. Kampis - Filippiadas/Tagmatarchou Velissariou
Continue to follow Epar.Od. Kampis - Filippiadas
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto the A5 ramp

Keep left at the fork and merge onto A5
Toll road
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto EO Artas Ioanninon/E951/EO5
Turn left onto Periferiaki Ioanninon (signs for Kozani/Kakavia/K. Pyrros Airport)
Turn right onto Epar.Od. Asfaka - Vrisochoriou (signs for Vikos Gorge/Central Zagori)
Turn right to stay on Epar.Od. Asfaka - Vrisochoriou (signs for Dilofo)
Turn left to stay on Epar.Od. Asfaka - Vrisochoriou
